Jan 10 (Reuters) - Kwantas Corporation Bhd:
* DEC PALM KERNEL EXPELLER PRODUCTION WAS 2,240.78 MT * DEC PALM KERNEL PRODUCTION 3,247.79 MT; DEC CRUDE PALM KERNEL OIL PRODUCTION 1,942.23 MT‍​
* DECEMBER PRODUCTION FFB 66,350.15 MT; DEC PRODUCTION OF CRUDE PALM OIL 13,738.49 MT‍​ Source text :( bit.ly/2CXgmpl ) Further company coverage: (bangalore.newsroom@thomsonreuters.com)
